itemLabel: Frederick Hamilton-Temple-Blackwood, 3rd Marquess of Dufferin and Ava

wikipedia_page.main: Frederick Temple Hamilton-Temple-Blackwood, 3rd Marquess of Dufferin and Ava,  (26 February 1875 – 21 July 1930), styled Lord Frederick Blackwood between 1888 and 1918, was a British soldier and politician. He died in an aircraft crash in 1930 at the age of 55.
